

Folders:
chemkin1D-GammaCurvefitted: generator for chemkin format
Foam1D-GammaCurvefitted: generator for foam format


Files:
***-GammaCurvefitted/soot1D/solveCoeffs1D_CFit.m: read abstract sectional reactions and expand them to elemental reactions.

***-GammaCurvefitted/soot1D/writeExpandReactions1D_CFit.m: write expanded reactions into foam/chemkin format.



Note:
lambda (porosity parameter) = Vfactor in ***-GammaCurvefitted/soot1D/CoagGamma_1D_CFit.m
To generator kinetics in different lambda, change the Vfactor. 
CoagGamma_1D.m is used to calculate fix temperature Gamma and does not affect the generated soot kinetics.




Other files:

gasReader1D.m reads the gas phase chemkin formattedted reactions.

FOAMwriter1D.m writes read data into foam format.

thermoReader.m read chemkin formatted thermo data.

thermoWriter.m write data into foam format in section
lumped species thermo parameters linearly scale from A4 depending on weight ratio.

thermoWriterNAPS.m write data into foam format in 1D section as imposed

GetSectionalSpInfo.m read the section arrangements, i.e. nC nH nHj and save them as SectionInfo



